rows.label: qev087405_MSG0001
rows.name: Strange. I was sure we'd find him here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0002
rows.name: ...So in other words, that's the nest they're coming from?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0003
rows.name:
If we know this level of detail,
how come we haven't eliminated them?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0004
rows.name: We've attempted two sweeps already.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0005
rows.name:
Both times, we lost soldiers and resources,
and gained absolutely nothing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0006
rows.name: I guess that explains all the damaged Skells from before.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0007
rows.name: The results of a failed mission...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0008
rows.name:
Still, until those indigens are cleared out,
our trade routes are threatened.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0010
rows.name:
Would you have us repeat the same mistake,
this time in a weakened state?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0011
rows.name: And how do you plan on funding this operation?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0012
rows.name: That isn't— Look, I realize we don't have the funds.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0013
rows.name: Boys, boys, knock it off already, will ya?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0014
rows.name: Commander?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0015
rows.name: Where'd he come from?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0016
rows.name: Just who do you think you're addressing?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0017
rows.name: I've seen that look before... You have a plan?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0018
rows.name: Wang's team spotted a pack leader in the area.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0019
rows.name: This ugly thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0020
rows.name: Take out the pack leader, the rest of 'em scatter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0021
rows.name: Any stragglers left over will make for easier targets.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0022
rows.name:
It sounds good in theory,
but how do you propose we deal with this pack leader?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0023
rows.name:
A concentrated strike with a team
of our very best and brightest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0024
rows.name: ...Them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0025
rows.name: Us?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0026
rows.name: Tatsu?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0027
rows.name: Hmm... Sounds interesting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0028
rows.name:
I guess that explains why they're
attending "top-secret" meetings.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0029
rows.name: Always a step ahead, eh, Commander?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0030
rows.name: What? No! We're just here to—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0031
rows.name: That's why you pay me the big bucks, am I right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0032
rows.name: Now wait just a minute![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0033
rows.name: Someone has to do this, Lin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0034
rows.name: I guess so, but still...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0035
rows.name: We'll take care of it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087405_MSG0036
rows.name: I knew you would.[ST:wait ]
